channel.title: In Need Of A Website Developer
channel.description:
Hey Mopar, I have been learning java for a while and i'm finally ready to start my own server. Now all I need is a website developer who can make a very nice looking site, I have a domain and I have tried using templates, but it's just not good enough. I don't want any rookie's, I need a GOOD Developer who can make a GOOD Site. What I want added can be discussed over skype. If you know what you are doing, PM me please.
Regards, Xevi
